# hexa-lang /.own — project-local SSOT layer (monotonic strengthening of hive .raw)
# 포맷: raw-format (.raw 와 동일 파서). 자세한 스펙: self/raw_loader.hexa
# 검증: ./build/hexa_stage0 tool/own_lint.hexa
#
# (빈 body — hexa-lang local rules 추가 시 own N <status> "<name>" + slug + enforce + why 형식)

own 1 live "parser format stability — raw_loader.hexa is API contract"
  slug parser-format-stability
  enforce self/raw_cli.hexa verify
  scope self/raw_loader.hexa
  why raw_loader.hexa is consumed by hive + nexus + airgenome + (self). Parser surface changes break cross-repo SSOT parsing — backward-compat semver applies.

own 2 live "AOT cache GC ω-cycle policy (raw 7 of L7 commit fcd087f0c)"
  slug aot-cache-policy
  enforce tool/aot_cache_gc.hexa
  scope .hexa-cache/
  why touch-on-access + prob 1% + audit ledger; lossless ω-cycle GC. project-local because cache layout is hexa-lang implementation detail.

# Migrated 2026-04-26 from hexa-lang/.raw — three self-host meta rules absorbed
# into project-local L1 layer. hexa-lang/.raw is retired; canonical L0 SSOT is
# now hive (github.com/need-singularity/hive). Original IDs: raw#1/2/3 -> own#3/4/5.

own 3 live "hexa-lang self-host fixpoint — parser-owner consumes own format"
  slug hexa-lang-self-host
  enforce self/raw_cli.hexa verify
  decl self/raw_loader.hexa
  scope hexa-lang/.own + hexa-lang/.doc (no .raw at root after 2026-04-26 migration to hive)
  why hexa-lang implements raw_loader.hexa — the parser FOR self-format DSL. raw_loader.hexa MUST round-trip parse self-host files as the implementation acceptance test.
  proof self/raw_cli.hexa verify --target hexa-lang/.own
  proof self/raw_cli.hexa verify --target hexa-lang/.doc
  severity block
  migrated-from raw 1 hexa-lang/.raw 2026-04-26

own 4 live "naming reconciliation — .commands -> .command (canonical)"
  slug naming-canonical
  status convention
  scope .commands -> .command, .chain (chain-kind extension), .raw-ref (sync metadata)
  why hexa-lang invented .commands (plural) before canonical .command (singular) was promoted across hive. Reconciliation landed 2026-04-26 (.commands -> .command, 11 cross-refs migrated).
  promoted-at 2026-04-26
  severity warn
  migrated-from raw 2 hexa-lang/.raw 2026-04-26

own 5 convention "follower-repo .raw-ref pattern — canonical mirror pin"
  slug raw-ref-follower
  enforce tool/raw_sync.hexa
  decl .raw-ref
  scope follower repos mirroring hive canonical .raw (contact, papers, anima, n6-architecture, nexus, void, airgenome, hexa-os, hexa-lang itself)
  format ref <N> <status> "<label>" + source + branch + path + pinned-hash + checked-at
  why follower repos pin to hive canonical .raw via .raw-ref (migrated 2026-04-26 from hexa-lang). tool/raw_sync.hexa (hexa-lang owns the tool) populates pinned-hash + checked-at; drift detection at sync time.
  proof tool/raw_sync.hexa check
  severity warn
  migrated-from raw 3 hexa-lang/.raw 2026-04-26
